---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Contractor Business Coaching - BuildRightPros">

  <!-- ============================================
       SECTION 1: HERO
       ============================================ -->
  <section id="hero" class="bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-50 to-gray-100 py-20">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 text-center">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Contractor Business Coaching That Gets Results</h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-700 mb-8">Expert guidance in sales, operations, financials, legal, social presence, networking, and website optimization - specifically for contractors</p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
        <a href="https://cal.com/buildrightpros" target="_blank" class="bg-blue-600 text-white px-8 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-blue-700 transition">Schedule Free Consultation</a>
        <a href="#services" class="border-2 border-blue-600 text-blue-600 px-8 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-blue-600 hover:text-white transition">View Coaching Programs</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ============================================
       SECTION 2: PROBLEM STATEMENT
       ============================================ -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-8 text-center">The Challenge Every Contractor Faces</h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <div class="bg-gray-50 border border-gray-200 rounded-xl p-6">
          <div class="text-orange-600 text-3xl mb-3">⚠️</div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">Too Many Hats, Not Enough Time</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">You're great at the trade - plumbing, HVAC, electrical, roofing. But running the business side? That's a different skillset entirely. Bidding, pricing, cash flow, legal compliance - it all takes time you don't have.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-gray-50 border border-gray-200 rounded-xl p-6">
          <div class="text-orange-600 text-3xl mb-3">💸</div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">Money Left on the Table</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Underpricing jobs, missing profit margins, poor cash flow management, and inefficient operations are costing you thousands every month. You know there's a better way - you just need someone to show you.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-gray-50 border border-gray-200 rounded-xl p-6">
          <div class="text-orange-600 text-3xl mb-3">📉</div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">Trial and Error Is Expensive</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Figuring it out alone means costly mistakes. Bad contracts, compliance issues, marketing that doesn't work, and systems that break down when you're busy. Every mistake sets you back months.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-gray-50 border border-gray-200 rounded-xl p-6">
          <div class="text-orange-600 text-3xl mb-3">🎯</div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">Missing Growth Opportunities</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Your competitors are getting better organized, systemizing their operations, and scaling. Without expert guidance, you're working harder but not growing faster. You need a proven roadmap to get ahead.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ============================================
       SECTION 3: COACHING SERVICES GRID
       ============================================ -->
  <section id="services" class="py-16 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4 text-center">Choose Your Coaching Path</h2>
      <p class="text-center text-gray-600 mb-12">Expert coaching tailored to the specific challenges contractors face</p>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        <!-- Sales Coaching -->
        <a href="/coaching/sales" class="bg-white border border-gray-300 rounded-xl p-6 hover:scale-105 hover:shadow-lg transition duration-300">
          <div class="text-blue-600 text-4xl mb-4">💼</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Sales Coaching</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Improve your close rates and build a sales process that actually works. Learn to qualify leads, present bids with confidence, and handle objections like a pro.</p>
          <span class="text-blue-600 font-semibold text-sm">Learn More →</span>
        </a>

        <!-- Operations Coaching -->
        <a href="/coaching/operations" class="bg-white border border-gray-300 rounded-xl p-6 hover:scale-105 hover:shadow-lg transition duration-300">
          <div class="text-blue-600 text-4xl mb-4">⚙️</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Operations Coaching</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Streamline your workflows and boost efficiency. Master project management, scheduling, crew coordination, and vendor relationships for smooth operations.</p>
          <span class="text-blue-600 font-semibold text-sm">Learn More →</span>
        </a>

        <!-- Financial Coaching -->
        <a href="/coaching/financial" class="bg-white border border-gray-300 rounded-xl p-6 hover:scale-105 hover:shadow-lg transition duration-300">
          <div class="text-blue-600 text-4xl mb-4">📊</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Financial Coaching</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Understand your numbers and maximize profitability. Job costing, pricing strategy, QuickBooks setup, profit margins, and cash flow management made simple.</p>
          <span class="text-blue-600 font-semibold text-sm">Learn More →</span>
        </a>

        <!-- Legal Coaching -->
        <a href="/coaching/legal" class="bg-white border border-gray-300 rounded-xl p-6 hover:scale-105 hover:shadow-lg transition duration-300">
          <div class="text-blue-600 text-4xl mb-4">⚖️</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Legal Coaching</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Protect your business with proper contracts and compliance. Navigate lien rights, insurance requirements, licensing, and dispute resolution with confidence.</p>
          <span class="text-blue-600 font-semibold text-sm">Learn More →</span>
        </a>

        <!-- Social Presence Coaching -->
        <a href="/coaching/social-presence" class="bg-white border border-gray-300 rounded-xl p-6 hover:scale-105 hover:shadow-lg transition duration-300">
          <div class="text-blue-600 text-4xl mb-4">📱</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Social Presence Coaching</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Build a strong online reputation that attracts customers. Optimize Facebook, Instagram, Google Business Profile, and manage reviews strategically.</p>
          <span class="text-blue-600 font-semibold text-sm">Learn More →</span>
        </a>

        <!-- Network Coaching -->
        <a href="/coaching/network" class="bg-white border border-gray-300 rounded-xl p-6 hover:scale-105 hover:shadow-lg transition duration-300">
          <div class="text-blue-600 text-4xl mb-4">🤝</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Network Coaching</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Generate referrals and build strategic partnerships. Connect with trade groups, develop a referral system, and create community relationships that fuel growth.</p>
          <span class="text-blue-600 font-semibold text-sm">Learn More →</span>
        </a>

        <!-- Website Coaching -->
        <a href="/coaching/website" class="bg-white border border-gray-300 rounded-xl p-6 hover:scale-105 hover:shadow-lg transition duration-300">
          <div class="text-blue-600 text-4xl mb-4">🌐</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Website Coaching</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Turn your website into a lead-generating machine. SEO optimization, mobile responsiveness, lead capture forms, and conversion rate optimization.</p>
          <span class="text-blue-600 font-semibold text-sm">Learn More →</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

